          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-100 mb-3 text-center">GitHub連携</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm text-center leading-relaxed">
            その日のCommitやPRを自動取得。<br>「何をしたっけ？」と思い出す時間をゼロにします。
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-24 bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-900 to-gray-800 overflow-hidden relative">
    <div class="absolute top-1/2 right-0 w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-indigo-900/20 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/2"></div>

    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-16 relative z-10">
      <div class="md:w-1/2">
        <span class="text-indigo-400 font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-xs border border-indigo-500/30 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-indigo-900/20">Seamless Integration</span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mt-6 mb-8 leading-tight text-white">
          「今日、何やったっけ？」<br>
          <span class="text-gray-400">その悩みはもう不要です。</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
          ボタンひとつで、あなたのGitHubアクティビティ（Commit, Issue, PR）を取得し、日報に自動挿入します。
          <br>正確な作業ログに基づいた、質の高い振り返りを体験してください。
        </p>
        
        <div class="bg-gray-900 rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-700 shadow-2xl backdrop-blur-sm bg-opacity-80">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-400 mb-5 border-b border-gray-800 pb-3">
            <span class="relative flex h-3 w-3">
              <span class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-green-400 opacity-75"></span>
              <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-3 w-3 bg-green-500"></span>
            </span>
            2025/11/21 の活動ログ
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-3 hover:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg transition cursor-default border border-transparent hover:border-gray-700">
              <span class="bg-purple-900/40 text-purple-300 text-xs px-2.5 py-1 rounded border border-purple-500/30 mt-0.5 font-mono">Merged</span>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-200">Feat: ゲストログイン機能の実装 (#42)</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-3 hover:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg transition cursor-default border border-transparent hover:border-gray-700">
              <span class="bg-blue-900/40 text-blue-300 text-xs px-2.5 py-1 rounded border border-blue-500/30 mt-0.5 font-mono">Commit</span>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-200">Fix: CIの環境変数設定を修正</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="md:w-1/2 relative w-full">
        <div class="absolute -inset-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-500 to-purple-600 rounded-2xl blur opacity-30"></div>
        <div class="relative bg-gray-800 rounded-2xl border border-gray-700 p-2 shadow-2xl">
            <div class="bg-gray-900 rounded-xl aspect-video flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-gray-600 border border-gray-800">
              <svg class="w-16 h-16 mb-4 opacity-30" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 16l4.586-4.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L16 16m-2-2l1.586-1.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L20 14m-6-6h.01M6 20h12a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"></path></svg>
              <span class="text-sm font-mono tracking-wider">App Screenshot Area</span>
            </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-24 bg-gray-900 border-t border-gray-800 relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/cubes.png')] opacity-5"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[800px] h-[300px] bg-green-900/20 rounded-full blur-[100px] pointer-events-none"></div>

    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center max-w-4xl relative z-10">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-8">開発の記録を、未来の資産に。</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-400 mb-12 text-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        DevJournalは、エンジニアによる、エンジニアのための日報アプリです。<br>
        まずはゲストログインで、機能をお試しください。
      </p>
      
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-5 justify-center">
         <%= button_to users_guest_sign_in_path, method: :post, data: { turbo: false }, class: "flex items-center justify-center w-full sm:w-auto px-12 py-5 bg-green-600 hover:bg-green-500 text-white text-lg font-bold rounded-xl shadow-xl shadow-green-900/40 transition transform hover:-translate-y-1 border border-green-500 ring-4 ring-green-900/20" do %>
          🚀 ゲストとして試す
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>